---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="How we review - Made the Weekend"
  description="Our first-hand rule, honest &quot;skip this&quot; calls, and how affiliate links work without bending the advice."
>
<section class="page-head">
  <div class="inner" style="max-width:760px;">
    <svg class="page-motif" width="120" height="44" viewBox="0 0 120 44" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <path d="M4 40 C 30 34, 40 22, 60 20 C 74 18.5, 82 17, 89 14" stroke="#E0A45C" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="0.5 7" opacity="0.8"></path>
  <path d="M98 2 C 101.3 2, 104 4.7, 104 8 C 104 12.5, 98 17.5, 98 17.5 C 98 17.5, 92 12.5, 92 8 C 92 4.7, 94.7 2, 98 2 Z" stroke="#E0A45C" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"></path>
  <circle cx="98" cy="7.8" r="1.8" fill="#E0A45C"></circle>
</svg>
    <p class="eyebrow">How we review</p>
    <h1>The rules behind every guide</h1>
    <p class="lede">A short, honest account of how we decide what to recommend - and how we make money without letting it bend the advice.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="light" style="padding-top:clamp(48px,7vw,72px);padding-bottom:clamp(64px,9vw,100px);">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:680px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">
    <h2 style="font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-weight:600;font-size:24px;color:var(--forest-deep);margin:0 0 12px;">First-hand or it doesn't go up</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 0 28px;">Every guide is based on a real visit. We stay the nights, walk the walks and eat the meals before writing a word. If nobody in our circle has genuinely been somewhere, there's no guide for it yet.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-weight:600;font-size:24px;color:var(--forest-deep);margin:0 0 12px;">We say when something's overrated</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 0 28px;">Recommendations only mean something if we're willing to warn you off things too. Every guide includes at least one honest "skip this" - the thing everyone suggests that isn't worth your weekend.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-weight:600;font-size:24px;color:var(--forest-deep);margin:0 0 12px;">How we make money</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 0 28px;">Some links to places to stay, tours and gear earn us a small commission if you book, at no extra cost to you. It never changes what we recommend or the order we recommend it in. We'd rather send you to the right place and earn nothing than the wrong place and earn a fee.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-weight:600;font-size:24px;color:var(--forest-deep);margin:0 0 12px;">Photography</h2>
    <p style="margin:0;">We use our own photos wherever we have them. Where we don't yet, we use properly licensed images as a clearly-marked stand-in and replace them with our own over time. We never pass off someone else's photo of a place as our own.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
</Base>
